&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is my status, from 272 messages, the library has detected Spanish 75% of times, plus some other messages. As you might infer, there are lot of languages listed there that I never used, so it’s really important to keep this values refreshing with higher message counts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For groups, this becomes even more interesting, as the message languages get updates for each user that speaks in the channel, giving ‘faster’, good results on the language being used:&lt;/p&gt;
